Newcomers that are in the process of join the Ev Community. Step 2 in the Ev Pathway
Triggers: Attended 3 times in 6 weeks OR Ticked "I'm New" (or "This is My Church" and haven't done Newish Connect) on their Connect Card.

Category for those who have put their trust in Jesus and are being nurtured in the early days of their faith.
